#QIIME2 Taxonomic Profiling Pipeline
Software Environment
QIIME2: 2021.2
DADA2 plugin (within QIIME2 2021.2)
Classifier: SILVA 138 (99% OTUs, 515F–806R region)

Raw FASTQ files (Single-End, Phred33)
│
├── 1. Data Import
│   Tool: qiime tools import
│   Output:
│       demux.qza
│
├── 2. Quality Check
│   Tool: qiime demux summarize
│   Output:
│       demux-summary.qzv
│
├── 3. Denoising (ASV Generation)
│   Tool: qiime dada2 denoise-single
│   Output:
│       table-dada2.qza
│       rep-seqs-dada2.qza
│       denoising-stats.qza
│
├── 4. Feature Filtering (Low abundance removal)
│   Tool: qiime feature-table filter-features
│   Output:
│       table-filtered.qza
│
├── 5. Feature Table Summary
│   Tool: qiime feature-table summarize
│   Output:
│       table.qzv
│
├── 6. Taxonomic Classification
│   Tool: qiime feature-classifier classify-sklearn
│   Database: SILVA 138 (99%, 515–806)
│   Output:
│       taxonomy.qza
│
├── 7. Taxonomy Visualization
│   Tool: qiime metadata tabulate
│   Output:
│       taxonomy.qzv
│
├── 8. Taxa Composition Barplots
│   Tool: qiime taxa barplot
│   Output:
│       taxa-bar-plots.qzv
│
├── 9. Phylogenetic Tree Construction
│   Tools:
│       qiime alignment mafft
│       qiime alignment mask
│       qiime phylogeny fasttree
│       qiime phylogeny midpoint-root
│
│   Outputs:
│       aligned-rep-seqs.qza
│       masked-aligned-rep-seqs.qza
│       rooted-tree.qza
│
├── 10. Alpha & Beta Diversity Analysis
│   Tool: qiime diversity core-metrics-phylogenetic
│   Output Directory:
│       core-metrics-results/
│           shannon_vector.qza
│           faith_pd_vector.qza
│           weighted_unifrac_distance_matrix.qza
│           weighted_unifrac_pcoa_results.qza
│           etc.
│
├── 11. Alpha Diversity Significance
│   Tool: qiime diversity alpha-group-significance
│   Output:
│       shannon-group-significance.qzv
│
├── 12. Beta Diversity Significance (PERMANOVA)
│   Tool: qiime diversity beta-group-significance
│   Output:
│       weighted-unifrac-permanova.qzv
│
└── 13. PCoA Visualization
    Tool: qiime emperor plot
    Output:
        weighted-unifrac-emperor.qzv

#Final Key Output Files

table-filtered.qza → Abundance table
taxonomy.qza → Taxonomic assignments
rooted-tree.qza → Phylogenetic tree
core-metrics-results/ → Diversity metrics
taxa-bar-plots.qzv → Composition visualization
